{"tid":226827,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"當看完這段片, 我覺得香港樓市會有排升","createTime":"2017-05-02T18:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T02:40:07.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ff2c3b4c7ef1c0e2508c32b3251186937861e6","tid":226827,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-4gXP-bvnmM&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-4gXP-bvnmM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EmowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=ae0b21a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-4gXP-bvnmM&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n裡面的數據都很有說服力<br />\n也反駁了一般市面上的無知說法<br />\n我覺得當中的數據是比較客觀的<br />\n<br />\n其實幾鍾意主持<br />\n拿出數據分析出結果, 而不是一開始支持或反對, 而是客觀看一件事"},{"pid":"65ede3152c59dff47e8e361aac8d86f0d533afef","tid":226827,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:38:29.000Z","msg":"講下入面既當中一些觀點<br />\n<br />\n1. 所謂既辣招, 根本無用<br />\n有樓既人唔會放, 做收租佬<br />\n而新增唔洗比稅的人每年有9萬個, 夠18歲/新移民等人仕"},{"pid":"fb1486f3ddf86e7560133063926988dffde6c6d3","tid":226827,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:40:30.000Z","msg":"2. 近年樓宅供應量跌左好多<br />\n07-13年, 每年落成量9666<br />\n84-97年, 每年平均落成量3萬個"},{"pid":"45d20cef89f4604d4804b7151a8cbe650521baf7","tid":226827,"uid":82466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:42:18.000Z","msg":"租樓秒秒賺"},{"pid":"01fac97817593137588c490a986205a78dea5ce6","tid":226827,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:42:28.000Z","msg":"3. 細價樓核爆效應<br />\n<br />\n細價樓好似白米咁剛需求, 而豪宅好似鮑蔘翅肚咁"},{"pid":"92091c31f1be68bf39075bfc822eb6f6ee97c61a","tid":226827,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:46:35.000Z","msg":"4. 供款佔入息比率<br />\n<br />\n有66%的人不用做按偈<br />\n點解66%可以不用做, 已累積財富(我們講的父幹母幹)/強國黑錢<br />\n<br />\n34%要做按偈<br />\n06年佔入息比率28.6%<br />\n16年佔入息比率19%<br />\n趨勢在下降中<br />\n<br />\n所以就咁睇無泡沫"},{"pid":"4287d9afadd785e6ef7ff7ead972ccaadc054ada","tid":226827,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"5. 新增加高收入人仕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n08-14年, 新增5萬或以上人仕有大約45萬個<br />\n每年新增宅住單位一萬幾個<br />\n<br />\n這些人已經足夠消費新增樓宅<br />\n這是個人計算, 仲未計家庭, 未計3, 4萬那一堆"},{"pid":"9e5e1dee8cbe419da77a0c9fae55f0a5add487bb","tid":226827,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:52:39.000Z","msg":"6. 已累積財富數目<br />\n<br />\n已累積財富數目不斷上升, 而供款比例在不斷下降"},{"pid":"e5e7e7f14a313730091256d324b2e0f6b4d82662","tid":226827,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:00:42.000Z","msg":"結論: 香港窮人會比人趕走, 廣東有錢人入主香港"},{"pid":"266a9213a6f5768911618b1109ab7e815511f50e","tid":226827,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結論: 香港窮人會比人趕走, 廣東有錢人入主香港</blockquote><br />\nno,係香港無論窮定有錢既人都會俾人趕走,大陸根本要地唔要人"},{"pid":"a0683b470bd380e92cd73c87522f4a8cb2ab2410","tid":226827,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結論: 香港窮人會比人趕走, 廣東有錢人入主香港</blockquote><br />\n樂觀SIR，咁我哋呢啲窮人可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d23908ef8b8ca236ce173b6ef3f5a86c4f16a9","tid":226827,"uid":21226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:45:28.000Z","msg":"最尾張圖都有啟示<br />\n跟著黎買有運行"},{"pid":"cded977261f1e064f87f3448c376df20bbbee0a2","tid":226827,"uid":113512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:40:07.000Z","msg":"即係無泡沫，樓市就算唔升，都唔好預佢會跌。<br />\n有樓的唔好賣樓，無樓但負擔到的快快買樓，無樓又無能力的香港已經唔適合你住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}